                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fudatou/">傅踢踢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-12-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读到2/3过后，渐渐体会到为什么是给孩子的诗了。蛮用心的，能让人从语言中醒来</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1017810552">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1017810552" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1017810552" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1017810552">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chaiyanchao/">Cycble</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-03-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">孩子读不读得懂不说，选取的内容多是想承载的太多，而又没有足够美。少数确实不错。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="828408182">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-828408182" class="vote-count">45</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-828408182" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="828408182">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Xenophon/">Xenophon</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-01-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">诗很好。但我总有个因浅陋而成的偏见：中国古典诗歌更适合孩子。音节、意象、意境，都可能比现代诗更契合孩子的心性。期待有古典修养深厚的人编一本《给孩子的诗之中国古典编》</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="829921748">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-829921748" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-829921748" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="829921748">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nianshixx/">年逝</a>
                    <span>2014-07-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这是要教给孩子啥啊 给大人缅怀下青春还行 外国的诗选的还算不错 国内那些真是呵呵呵</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="833611387">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
